{"tid":811980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★高鐵西九站旁路面下陷20厘米　圓方商舖指裂到落唔到閘","createTime":"2018-09-09T09:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T11:37:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"390a9b6b38eda1c1230ce736ae6d43913005f93f","tid":811980,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:35:15.000Z","msg":"廣深港高鐵香港段本月23日通車，懷疑沉降事件仍然是沒完沒了。傳真社報道指，鄰近西九龍站的圓方商場疑受工程影響出現沉降，建築物內牆身出現多道裂紋，面向高鐵站的漾日居基座小巴站外路面更下陷逾20厘米。港鐵回覆傳真社指，有關範圍的沉降數值未有超出需要即時停工的指標，施工期間一直沒有對附近建築物安全構成影響的報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180909/bkn-20180909134930825-0909_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180909%2Fbkn-20180909134930825-0909_00822_001.html&d=SuDdN0eGUOeRjBjatkZNKdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b469af1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180909/bkn-20180909134930825-0909_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f71d52ef0399a77dcb81677d5c44f467fe4d8034","tid":811980,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180909/photo/bkn-20180909134930825-0909_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180909172553\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180909%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180909134930825-0909_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180909172553&h=1c7cd15e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1be16159d3bf751dd3abe45e350ead3566f5b5e","tid":811980,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29fb024b28637bc33b5d39dac1b36928021b3a0","tid":811980,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:36:33.000Z","msg":"圓方店舖工作的職員向傳真社指出，員工休息室的地面及牆身3年前已出現裂紋，更試過因裂紋而「落唔到閘」，但現時圓方商場的店舖及走廊牆身均以<span style=\"color: red;\">雲石等裝飾遮蓋</span>，難以查證。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets